            <a name="about"></a>
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <p class="text-white mx-3">Hi, I am a Software Engineering undergraduate at <a class="anchors" href="https://hit.ac.zw">Harare Institute of Technology</a>, with keen interests in mobile application development and more specifically with the Flutter Framework. I have worked on a few <a href="https://github.com/iamngoni" class="anchors">projects</a> in web development, desktop systems development, mobile app development and task automation cli tools. I love developing products and models that empower man.</p>
